WEBVTT

01:09:07.274 --> 01:09:09.441
Let me check
if that boy got married.

01:09:09.483 --> 01:09:11.524
Even if that doesn't work out,
I have other options.

01:09:11.774 --> 01:09:13.108
Anyway, the sooner the better.

01:09:13.149 --> 01:09:14.149
Right.

01:09:14.274 --> 01:09:17.566
And one more thing... Let's not
discuss this over the phone anymore.

01:09:17.816 --> 01:09:18.899
We'll talk in person.
